subSubSection.paragraph:
Male genitalia
: As as in generic description. Genital capsule (
Fig. 67
): Broadly rounded, with three large ventral processes arising between parameres. Left paramere (
Fig. 68
) slender, somewhat C-shaped, with apex recurved. Right paramere (
Fig. 69
) elongate slender, S-shaped, with, apex sharply recurved.
